    "120935297": {
      "title": "Relativistic Coulomb excitation",
      "abstract": "Abstract Coulomb excitation of both target and projectile in relativistic heavy ion collisions is evaluated including the lowest order correction for the deviation from a straight line trajectory. Explicit results for differential and total cross sections are given in the form of tables and figures."
